\begin_layout Section
Occupancy Matrix
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The Occupancy Matrix is a quick glance view of room occupancy.
 The date select and range controls are on top.
 The room lanes show a visual histogram of rooms vs dates.
 The room lane shows the first 2 letters of the last name of the primary
 guest.
 Clicking on a room lane will retrieve basic guest information and reservation
 information and a link to additional information and full guest profile
 will display and all rooms associated with the selected date will be highlighte
d in red.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
Date Select and Range
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The date axis has 3 controls:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
The calendar select will adjust the dates on the horizontal date axis.
 The date selected on the calendar will be the starting date.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Clicking on any of the dates will push the start of the date line to (day
 - 4) of the selected date.
 If the first date is clicked the date line will move forward.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
The slider will adjust the number of days represented up to 30 days.
 It will not affect the starting date.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
Room Lanes
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Room lanes are color coded for easy identification.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsubsection
Color Coding
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The meaning and variety of colors are all customized from the configuration
 screen.
 Room status can be realized with just a glance and historical room states
 can be accessed and visualized as well.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsubsection
Room Highlighting
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Selecting a room will highlight it and any other rooms on that particular
 reservation.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Section
Reservation Viewer
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Graphics
	filename img/image309.png
	width 10cm

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Clicking on a room in the room lane will display a condensed room information
 block.
 This allows rapid review of reservations on the Occupancy Matrix.
 Clicking on the Reservation link in the view will open a full Guest and
 Reservations section.
\end_layout

